{
  "stem": "1511.3",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When they were hiding, it was after Yom Kippur-- Yom Kippur.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "After Yom Kippur night, my mother says she's going to go out.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Maybe something's left in the house.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She's going to bring anything, some water just to keep them going.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She went out, and Usher went with her, my brother went with her.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And as she won out, the Polack, somebody saw her, reported right away to the German.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they didn't take 10 minutes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they knew that already.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They saw that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my mother went hiding under-- under the house.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was actually not a house.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was also something for chickens.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my brother climbed up on the wall, on the roof.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "On the roof.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he flat lay.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they pulled my mother out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They couldn't find him, and they shot her right on the spot.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she had a lot of jewelry, whatever we had from-- the golden watch, whatever we had from the house.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Everything she had hidden on her back in there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there's everything they didn't.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But when they saw the kids later, they got very scared.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they came out of this bunker, and then all of them, everybody around to a different place.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And my auntie went also out, and they caught her with her little son.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they shot them, too, but one of the daughters, Rifka, she went with mine family.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Rifka and Chanale, they were hiding in them, and they pulled them in.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And when they came to-- they went to hide someplace.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they found a place by a Gentile guy.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was the worst Jewish enemy, and I remember his name was Szczur.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Szczur is something with a mouse in Polish, but the bigger one, the rat.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "A rat.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
